{"tid":1954282,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"今個學期唔洗再返學?","createTime":"2020-04-01T16:58:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-01T17:19:49.000Z","uid":344793,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"eb6f5dcc0bfff73a1009d70fe5b7cfff2f26385e","tid":1954282,"uid":344793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T16:58:06.000Z","msg":"【全城禁聚】政府最新評估「禁聚令」或延長14日 料本學年全報銷<br />\n<br />\n本港疫情非常嚴峻，每日有數十宗確診個案。政府近日再評估一系列新措施，包括剛於3月29日凌晨開始實施的「禁聚令」。據悉，因應疫情未有紓緩迹象，政府初步評估，<span style=\"color: red;\">很可能於禁聚令實施的首階段14日後，把有關措施再延長多14日</span>。另外，因為公立醫院隔離病床不足，駿洋邨將會接收公院內病情輕微的確診病人，以騰出第一線負壓病床。<span style=\"color: red;\">今年夏天前相信亦不會復課。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200402/QXZHBIQHZX4DPWYFMVM37VY664/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200402%2FQXZHBIQHZX4DPWYFMVM37VY664%2F&d=qkncW4ahWQk%2FJA9l97O%2FUsTiFwqRwBg1VWT7Je45URE%3D&h=5e5ecafb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200402%2FQXZHBIQHZX4DPWYFMVM37VY664%2F&h=5854156d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200402/QXZHBIQHZX4DPWYFMVM37VY664/</a>"},{"pid":"b9514a08c5623d222fea312854bad1a9e5c2e874","tid":1954282,"uid":66365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T16:59:00.000Z","msg":"dsa 點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7083baaefe7c36d7d0c18501360672ab1c0bc7d","tid":1954282,"uid":66365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T16:59:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>dse點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"9e69d42cd0e810210044ebb06b0043192f9bae7f","tid":1954282,"uid":42804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d7083baaefe7c36d7d0c18501360672ab1c0bc7d","tid":1954282,"uid":66365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T16:59:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>dse點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T17:02:54.000Z","msg":"分分鐘畀你考完，放榜後大學唔開，收唔到生，等到解禁後，呢一批學生同下一年應屆考生撞埋一齊，到時呢批考生就會搶埋上年考生個學位。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"018e49f9bd5732843c10919afdd5cf47f38290a8","tid":1954282,"uid":67425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T17:03:16.000Z","msg":"考天才波"},{"pid":"47dea2b7b765ed55deda802dd9bd137d60e356b0","tid":1954282,"uid":123308,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T17:19:49.000Z","msg":"re-post with edit:<br />\n<br />\n個人認為，課堂可以唔使面對面上，因為而家個個都識網上 online video conferencing<br />\n貌似停課，但其實根本冇所謂「復課與否」嘅問題，<br />\n因為學與教從來冇停過，只係形式改變咗，變咗 virtual distance learning，<br />\n全世界教學界而家呢個時期都係咁<br />\n有人話可能咁樣可能學唔到嘢，又唔知啲學生聽唔聽到書，<br />\n但其實你就算 face-to-face 教學，你都唔能夠確保學生冇遊魂<br />\n要走堂嘅，要做自己嘢嘅，始終都會唔留心<br />\n有嘢要問，自然會搵老師，相信老師都會私下 text / video 覆你，<br />\n只不過係形式唔係 face-to-face 咁解，本質冇變<br />\n<br />\n大學方面，就算 video conference 形式上堂，<br />\n同現實上 lecture 都係差唔多，都係去到坐完就走，<br />\n除非你有問題留低問，否則都只係形式上有分別 (real vs virtual)，本質上無異<br />\n<br />\n至於公開考試方面，我認為考試點都要考，<br />\n因為始終須要一個評核準則，重點係可以畀學生升學時，對方有一個公開考試參照<br />\n<br />\n冇錯，係，就算係考試，都有機會有誤差，<br />\n但起碼 HKDSE 至少有兩個 markers + 你鍾意可以加錢 appeal<br />\n如果只計平時分，真係咁多間中學，間間把尺都唔同，誤差極大，<br />\n有機會埋沒咗最後考試發力嘅學生<br />\n（亦間接警世：千祈唔好最後留力，唔係就會好似今屆咁樣，變數極大，囉囉攣）<br />\n<br />\nSpeaking 又係一個問題，如果筆試考試照樣進行，點解唔可以一樣做埋 speaking？<br />\n都係一個課室考，兩個 markers、四個 candidates，君不見危險程度會比筆試高<br />\n頂多係須要多啲 waiting room，隔疏啲人<br />\n不論係咩語文，都係在乎聽說讀寫，缺一不可，<br />\n冇咗 speaking 呢個 output，得返 writing，<br />\n對 writing 差但 speaking 得嘅學生，無疑係被監生質低咗原本應有嘅 performance<br />\n<br />\n利申：相關工作"}]}